# Pre-Commit Quality (CRITICAL)

## Before Every Commit

1. **Build** – Run the build and ensure it succeeds.
2. **Run tests** – Execute the full test suite before committing.
3. **Code coverage** – Check coverage; add tests for any new functionality so it is covered.

## Commit Messages

- **Never** include "made by cursor", "generated by cursor", or similar AI attribution in commit messages.
- Keep messages clear and professional.
